- if postcode
  %h2
    Postcode
    %strong= postcode
    not found

  %p Sorry, we couldn't find that postcode.
  %p
    If you’re sure this postcode exists please
    = mail_to Rails.configuration.contact_email, "contact us"
    to let us know.
- else
  %h2 No results found
  %p
    Sorry, we couldn't find any people, policies or divisions relevant to your search term
    %strong “#{params[:query]}”.
  %p
    Suggestions:

  %ul
    %li check the spelling
    %li try some more general or alternate terms
